'''Taskla''' tga yan wanaw g usiwel anafgan f tugett n tufrayin d iswingimen d yimyan d iferfuden nns s yat tɣarast tamawant n tirra, seg uzuzzer, s tmedyazt, s umareg, afad ad yaf ufgan taɣarast nna t issusumen ad srs isawel f tɣawsiwin i yas igan anezgum, nɣ iɣ ur iẓḍar awedkra n wanaw yaḍni ad isawel fellas. Tella dar tsekla yat tezdayt meqquṛn d tutlayt, acku tayafut n kra n tutlayt ar tt nttafa g tussna nns ittyuran, nɣ ittusmattin s yimi zzɣ tasut s tayyaḍ zund tutlayt nnɣ Tamaziɣt, d ar ttuḥḍa ttussna yad g mnnaw n wanawen n tsekla, ukan ar ttmzaray s idɣaren d izmazz, d ar bedda gis ittili kra n umzaray d usmaynu s uzray n yizmazz. Llan t kigan n tewnnatin f mad igan tasekla d ɣikelli is inna Wilyam Haẓelt (Tasekla n kraygat tmetti  ad igan tisit n iswingimen nns).

Ar iddenkay uzuzzer (Nnater s tesrɣint) zzɣ tirra i ur iṭṭafen awed kra n unuɣ unṣib i srs ittuẓlan nɣ nttan ad ur igin tamedyazt. Amma Tamedyazt nɣ Amareg ar gis ittarem umedyaz s uncek nna mmu yeẓḍaṛ ad gis isfalki awal d tguriwin d ad issemres tiɣarasin tisṛqqiyin tisfalkayin d ussemres n tmeɣrutin.

